   <identificationInfo>
      <resourceName>Polish Named Entity Resources</resourceName>
      <description>The Polish Named Entity Resources have been obtained from existing sources and supplemented with additional language-specific resources acquired from the Web. Whenever appropriate, inflected forms were generated using Morfeusz SGJP generator. The Polish Named Entity Resource data was used in the process of named entity annotation of the National Corpus of Polish (NKJP).

The following hierarchy of names is used: forenames and surnames, city, country, mountain, region and river names, institution names, relational adjectives and inhabitant names stemming from country names, named entity triggers (months, days, positions, etc.)</description>
